descriptionHtml:
Got bored and left the modding scene for a bit, but im back with more Skyrim models.

Models:
Dishonored City Watch Sword
Dishonored Corvo's Sword - In the works


Permission & Uses
Use the models as you wish as long as credit is given.

Requests:
If you have a request message me and I might consider it, I do this as a hobby so my time is limited to either working on my own stuff or requested models. I have no problem with weapons and shields, I do not like armor it takes to long to make, clutter and random objects are fine as long as they are not overly complex. If you do request something please link reference images.
